*A scheduled Beer Drinking contest between [[Matt Hardy]] and [[Alvin Burke, Jr.|Montel Vontavious Porter]] was cancelled after Hardy's replacement, [[Stone Cold Steve Austin]] delivered a [[Stunner (professional wrestling)|Stone Cold Stunner]] to MVP.<ref name="MVP vs Austin"/>
*'''[[John Hennigan|John Morrison]] defeated [[CM Punk]] to retain the [[ECW Championship]] (7:07)'''<ref name="SLAM! Review"/><ref name="SummerSlam - Morrison vs Punk"/><ref name="SS WrestleView Report"/>
**Morrison pinned Punk by putting his feet on the ropes for extra leverage.
*'''[[Triple H]] defeated [[Booker Huffman|King Booker]] (w/[[Sharmell Sullivan|Queen Sharmell]]) (7:56)'''<ref name="SLAM! Review"/><ref name="HHH vs Booker"/><ref name="SS WrestleView Report"/>
** Triple H pinned Booker after a [[Facebuster#Double underhook facebuster|Pedigree]].
*'''[[Dave Bautista|Batista]] defeated [[World Heavyweight Championship (WWE)|World Heavyweight Champion]] [[The Great Khali]] (w/Ranjin Singh) by disqualification (6:57)'''<ref name="SLAM! Review"/><ref name="SummerSlam - Khali vs Batista"/><ref name="SS WrestleView Report"/>
**Khali was disqualified after he hit Batista with a steel chair. As a result, Khali retained the title.
*'''[[John Cena]] defeated [[Randy Orton]] to retain the [[WWE Championship]] (21:19)'''<ref name="SLAM! Review"/><ref name="SummerSlam - Orton vs Cena"/><ref name="SS WrestleView Report"/>
**Cena pinned Orton after an [[Professional wrestling throws#Fireman's carry takeover|FU]].

